  "prompt": "Which is a suitable inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center near Warren County IL?",
  "response": "Finding a suitable inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center involves considering factors such as the type of treatment offered, the environment, and the specific needs of the individual seeking help. While I can provide general guidance, it's best to consult directly with healthcare professionals or local resources for the most accurate and personalized advice. Here are some options you might consider:\n\n1. **Bridgeway Inc.** - Located in nearby Galesburg, IL, Bridgeway offers behavioral health services that might include addiction treatment programs.\n\n2. **Riverside Treatment Center** - Based in Macomb, IL, this center offers substance abuse treatment services.\n\n3. **UnityPoint Health \u2013 Robert Young Center** - Located in Rock Island, IL, this center provides a range of mental health and substance abuse services.\n\nEnsure you contact these centers directly to inquire about the specific inpatient programs they offer, their treatment approaches, and whether they are a good fit for your needs. Additionally, you might want to consult with a healthcare provider for recommendations tailored to the individual's specific situation.",
